{
  "stem": "13096.6",
  "chunk_idx": 13,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And like us, all the other 20 people, they were there.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Some, you know, came to Africa.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Some, they had relative in America.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And they start, you know, inquiring, and sending messages through the Red Cross, because, at the time, the post they were unbelievable.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You can send a letter and it arrive now in two days.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It was maybe two months before you can get.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But to give us courage, they were sending, you know, by-- you know, by telegram through the Red Cross, even money, my thing.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And one thing we will never forget in our life, never, we are very, very grateful to the American nation, you know, the American Jews.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They did whatever they do, because in their place, they were quicker to send us help.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Our crowd, you know, here, in Belgian Congo and in South Africa, there were so many Jews that were trying to help.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But they would find difficulty in the arrangement.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "But the American people, straight away they form, you know, society, like the [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "They call the Joint.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "You know, they were very, very-- very, very quick to send us help in kind and in money.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And also, you know, the American soldiers that they were Jews, you know, they were trying-- you know, they were in [NON-ENGLISH], nearby Bologna and other places few kilometers away.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Whenever they'd leave, those American Jewish boys, they will come to the rabbi-- you know, to the rabbi house to visit the refugee, you know, girls.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "They were really wonderful.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "That's why, you know, in my heart, I keep-- as I keep Israel, I keep America in my heart, like my-- you know-- I can't explain.",
      "word_count": 26
    }
  ],
